<P1para>
<Text>In regulation 4 of the Social Security (Disability Living Allowance) Regulations 1991<FootnoteRef Ref="f00049"/> (rate of benefit)—</Text>
<P3 DocumentURI="http://www.legislation.gov.uk/uksi/2026/148/article/14/a/made" IdURI="http://www.legislation.gov.uk/id/uksi/2026/148/article/14/a" id="article-14-a">
<Pnumber>a</Pnumber>
<P3para>
<Text>in paragraph (1)(a) for “£110.40” substitute <InlineAmendment>“£114.60”</InlineAmendment>;</Text>
</P3para>
</P3>
<P3 DocumentURI="http://www.legislation.gov.uk/uksi/2026/148/article/14/b/made" IdURI="http://www.legislation.gov.uk/id/uksi/2026/148/article/14/b" id="article-14-b">
<Pnumber>b</Pnumber>
